Uninstalling
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Paperwork can be uninstalled.
 Uninstalling Paperwork 
\emph on
won't
\emph default
 remove your work directory or documents.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Windows
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
GNU/Linux
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
If you installed Paperwork manually:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Verbatim
sudo pip uninstall paperwork
\end_layout

\begin_layout Verbatim
sudo pip uninstall pyocr
\end_layout

\begin_layout Verbatim
sudo pip uninstall pyinsane
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
(it's python-pip on some systems)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
If you installed many versions of these packages, you may have to run these
 commands many times.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Note that there are other dependencies installed with Paperwork.
 However, python-pip can't detect and remove automatically unused dependencies.
 This is why you should use your distribution package(s) if possible.
\end_layout

